dc_title_s: Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Pipelines in the United States, Fall 2012
dc_description_s: This line dataset represents locations of existing and proposed CO2 pipelines in the United States. This layer includes data for all interstate pipelines and major intrastate pipelines for the fall quarter of 2012.This layer is intended to assist users in locating and analyzing carbon dioxide pipeline data in the United States and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
